    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Overview</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Navicula Meatus</strong> is a dark and surreal puzzle-adventure game set in a peculiar world of murky alleys and fleshy growths. Explore a decaying town shrouded in mystery, interact with its charming denizens. Become a crustacean and utilise the unique puzzle-crawler grid-based meat systems. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203590/extras/da42bea74a868a71093e805950d821b0.webp?t=1745570672\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203590/extras/da42bea74a868a71093e805950d821b0.poster.avif?t=1745570672\" class=\"bb_img\" width=256 height=256 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore:</strong> The decaying town where the sinews of ruined buildings throb while grotesque beings beckon you to the alleys. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unravel:</strong> The lurching cryptograms of the <i>Navicula Meatus</i>, become entangled in the cumbersome user interface. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bereft of Guidance:</strong> Human language has been surgically removed from the experience. Fun and gameplay have also been excised to allow for pure streamlined immersion. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unstable Surroundings:</strong> The meat-glue binding the world is fragile so repeated playthroughs will present new disfigurements, including: </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Flute Boy:</strong> A wretched street urchin whose amusing melodies will thrill you as you linger, soaked in the sublime ambience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >    <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203590/extras/60694b0e88c8ae2acbabc50f76077624.poster.avif?t=1745570672\" width=256 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203590/extras/60694b0e88c8ae2acbabc50f76077624.webm?t=1745570672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
